feat: integrate Felo role management in Discord bot
- Add `DISCORD_FELO_ROLE_ID` environment variable in Dockerfile - Import `Client` from serenity_prelude in discord.rs - Change `init` function in discord.rs to return `Client` and start it outside the function - Add `discord_felo_role_id` field to `FeloHandler` struct in felo_handler.rs - Implement `start`, `get_pro_list`, `parse_pro_list`, `prepare_data_for_review_discord_users`, `review`, `adjust_discord_role`, and `review_discord_users` functions in `FeloHandler` struct - Add new tests for `get_bindings`, `review`, and `review_discord_users` functions in felo_handler.rs - Modify `init` function in lib.rs to start the discord client and pass the HTTP client to `FeloHandler`
